name: Welcome to Scavenger Bunker
description:
Kimchee a.k.a The Caracal, the young member of Alley Katz, living at Route 8O8 in his bunker with 1000 games inside. He snatched all the games when he still in "Urban Scavenger", the most mischievous gang in Main City.

His bunker named Pitfall, because when someone tried to sneak in, Kimchee guaranteed that person will never find the bunker main hall or exit. Kimchee build a labyrinth & sets many trap in there, so it's very necessary if anyone who wants to come & meet Kimchee inside it's better doing a private call with Kimchee, he will guide you for sure.

The reason why he wear the bandana that way because Kimchee wants to be like a legend 2pac. Also he always said "Tomorrow I wake with second wind and strong because of pride. I know I fought with all my heart to keep the dream alive."

With that quotes, he agreed to leave Urban Scavenger & create his own gang with his childhood friends who known as Alley Katz from Route 8O8.

What kind of action they will do? We will see it as soon as possible.
